---
import { Heart, Shield, TrendingUp } from 'lucide-react';
---

<!-- Features Grid Section -->
<section class="py-16 md:py-24 bg-gray-50/30">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="text-center mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-extrabold text-gray-900 mb-4">
        なぜ UMUO が選ばれるのか
      </h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 text-lg max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        最新の AI 技術で、賢いショッピングをサポートします
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      <!-- Feature 1 -->
      <div
        class="relative p-8 md:p-10 rounded-[2.5rem] bg-white border border-gray-100 shadow-sm hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-500 group"
      >
        <div
          class="w-16 h-16 bg-primary-100 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-8 group-hover:scale-110 group-hover:rotate-3 transition-transform duration-500"
        >
          <TrendingUp className="w-8 h-8 text-primary-600" />
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold mb-4">リアルタイム比較</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-500 leading-relaxed">
          主要ECサイトの価格をリアルタイムで取得。常に最新の最安値をお届けします。
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Feature 2 -->
      <div
        class="relative p-8 md:p-10 rounded-[2.5rem] bg-white border border-gray-100 shadow-sm hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-500 group"
      >
        <div
          class="w-16 h-16 bg-secondary-100 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-8 group-hover:scale-110 group-hover:rotate-3 transition-transform duration-500"
        >
          <Shield className="w-8 h-8 text-secondary-600" />
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold mb-4">安心の正規品判定</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-500 leading-relaxed">
          AIがショップの信頼性を独自に評価。偽物や悪質業者を徹底排除します。
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Feature 3 -->
      <div
        class="relative p-8 md:p-10 rounded-[2.5rem] bg-white border border-gray-100 shadow-sm hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-500 group"
      >
        <div
          class="w-16 h-16 bg-purple-100 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-8 group-hover:scale-110 group-hover:rotate-3 transition-transform duration-500"
        >
          <Heart className="w-8 h-8 text-purple-600" />
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold mb-4">学割・クーポン自動適用</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-500 leading-relaxed">
          学割や期間限定クーポン情報を自動で探し出し、実質価格で比較します。
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
